Author: alessF
Text: You need to chill. Really. I read your post, no one attacked you, they just told you that it’s fine if your friends wants to go out and eat, they invite you to include you, you don’t have to eat if you don’t want but you don’t have to be a bitch because they want to do something that’s totally normal to non disordered people. Nobody wants to make you feel bad, don’t let your ed brain to mess with your social life irl and online.
